title: Joe List: The Boston Garbage
description: Comedian Joe List joins us to talk about growing up outside of Boston, stand up comedy, and what makes a family trashy. You may know Joe List from Netflix, Joe Rogan Podcast, Tuesdays with Stories, Letterman and Comedy Central. Subscribe. Rate & Review.
